[32m+[m[32m# Corridor Classification Doctrine[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mStatus: doctrine and read-only type alignment.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Constitutional Rule[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCorridor classification describes development intent. It does not create ScopeVersion truth, routing authority, Prism score authority, or execution authority.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mScopeVersion remains execution truth. Route Engineering remains the authority that converts reviewed corridor evidence into executable network truth.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Purpose[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mCorridor classification separates physical length from network role.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mA corridor may be long in miles and still be metro if it connects many local aggregation points inside one MSA. A short corridor may be strategic interconnection if it connects a cloud on-ramp, IX, meet-me room, or carrier hotel.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Classification Layers[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mClassification has three advisory layers:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass`: broad corridor family such as `METRO`, `MIDDLE_MILE`, `LONGHAUL`, `AI_CORRIDOR`, or `INTERCONNECTION`.[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole`: functional role such as `METRO_AGGREGATION`, `MSA_INTERCONNECT`, `BACKBONE_INTERCONNECT`, or `AI_FABRIC`.[m
[32m+[m[32m- `aggregationRole`: what the corridor aggregates or hands off, such as LSOs, AI compute, data centers, regional POPs, campus buildings, or interconnection points.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Distance Doctrine[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDistance is evidence, not classification authority.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDistance may influence confidence and warnings, but distance alone must not override:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- MSA context.[m
[32m+[m[32m- endpoint role.[m
[32m+[m[32m- customer intent.[m
[32m+[m[32m- aggregation function.[m
[32m+[m[32m- interconnection purpose.[m
[32m+[m[32m- AI fabric purpose.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mExample: a 165-mile route connecting 26 LSOs inside one MSA is `METRO_AGGREGATION` / `METRO`, not longhaul.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## AI Corridor Doctrine[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m`AI_CORRIDOR` may operate as an overlay on geography.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mWhen AI, GPU, hyperscaler, neocloud, substation, transmission, or power-proximity evidence dominates, the network role may be `AI_FABRIC` while the underlying physical class remains metro, middle-mile, regional, or longhaul evidence.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Authority Boundary[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe classification engine may emit diagnostics, confidence, and warnings. It may not:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- call routing providers.[m
[32m+[m[32m- score candidates.[m
[32m+[m[32m- persist corridor truth.[m
[32m+[m[32m- create ScopeVersions.[m
[32m+[m[32m- approve promotion.[m
[32m+[m[32m- modify lifecycle state.[m
[32m+[m
