[32m+[m[32m# Corridor Classification Rules[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mStatus: read-only classification doctrine.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Rule Priority[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe classifier evaluates role signals in this order:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m1. Explicit hints, when provided.[m
[32m+[m[32m2. Campus/facility signals.[m
[32m+[m[32m3. Interconnection handoff signals.[m
[32m+[m[32m4. AI fabric signals.[m
[32m+[m[32m5. Backbone or transport-heavy signals.[m
[32m+[m[32m6. Same-MSA aggregation signals.[m
[32m+[m[32m7. MSA-to-MSA relationship.[m
[32m+[m[32m8. Regional-to-MSA relationship.[m
[32m+[m[32m9. Default regional classification.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Same-MSA Metro Aggregation[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf the corridor is inside the same MSA and evidence includes LSOs, carrier hotels, data centers, IX, enterprise, wireless, municipal, utility, or aggregation language, classify as:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole = METRO_AGGREGATION`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass = METRO`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mDistance is advisory only.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## MSA-to-MSA Interconnect[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf A and Z MSAs are known and different, classify as:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole = MSA_INTERCONNECT`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass = MIDDLE_MILE`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32munless stronger backbone or AI fabric evidence is present.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Backbone Interconnect[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf evidence includes backbone, longhaul, transport backbone, regional POP, carrier hotel, DWDM, wave, transport, terabit, or intercity intent, classify as:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole = BACKBONE_INTERCONNECT`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass = LONGHAUL`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## AI Fabric[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf evidence includes AI, GPU, hyperscaler, neocloud, substation, transmission, power, or AI compute intent, classify as:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole = AI_FABRIC`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass = AI_CORRIDOR`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe result may preserve an `underlyingCorridorClass` inferred from geography.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Campus[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf evidence indicates internal campus, building, facility, meet-me room, MMR, internal entrance, or campus distribution, classify as:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole = CAMPUS`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass = CAMPUS`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Interconnection[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIf evidence indicates cloud on-ramp, IX, meet-me, carrier hotel handoff, or cross-connect purpose, classify as:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `networkRole = INTERCONNECTION`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `corridorClass = INTERCONNECTION`[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m## Diagnostics[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe classifier emits:[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- `[CORRIDOR_CLASSIFICATION_STARTED]`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `[CORRIDOR_ROLE_INFERRED]`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `[CORRIDOR_MSA_RELATIONSHIP_INFERRED]`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `[CORRIDOR_AGGREGATION_ROLE_INFERRED]`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `[CORRIDOR_CLASSIFICATION_WARNING]`[m
[32m+[m[32m- `[CORRIDOR_CLASSIFICATION_COMPLETE]`[m
[32m+[m
